    <note>Zhao(1) Zhongcan [22431] Fan Zuyu, WJ, 51.15b-17a (wife, born Yang(2), who was only twenty when Zhongcan died--at this time she had had two sons (only one survived to receive a mingzi) and two daughters. Despite suggestions that she remarry, she remained a chaste widow until she died in 1090 at age 50). Even though only one son survived, the imperial clan genealogy records extensive descendants of this son. SS(PRC), 224.6563. CBD, 4, 3467.</note>
